You know, I used to make
a great soup out of that.

1598
01:18:02,443 --> 01:18:03,603
- What, really?
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

1599
01:18:03,603 --> 01:18:04,523
- Can you teach me that?
- Yeah, one day.

